figuring out what it does

00:10:58.520 --> 00:10:59.750
and whether I'd like it.

00:10:59.750 --> 00:11:02.090
And we'd like to help users
learn more about the game

00:11:02.090 --> 00:11:04.340
before the download.

00:11:04.340 --> 00:11:06.620
One way we're doing
this is exposing users

00:11:06.620 --> 00:11:09.500
to more of your gameplay
earlier in the funnel

00:11:09.500 --> 00:11:11.240
through inline videos.

00:11:11.240 --> 00:11:14.450
