game's home page of the store.

00:11:14.450 --> 00:11:16.850
And in addition to
the usual icons,

00:11:16.850 --> 00:11:19.670
users will be able to browse
a set of videos for games

00:11:19.670 --> 00:11:21.860
that we think they
will really like.

00:11:21.860 --> 00:11:24.260
We're doing a similar test
for screenshots inline,

00:11:24.260 --> 00:11:27.397
which will show up in the search
results and in the home page.

00:11:27.397 --> 00:11:29.480
These features are designed
to simplify the search

00:11:29.480 --> 00:11:31.520
and discovery experience
by giving users

00:11:31.520 --> 00:11:34.220
a preview of what they're going
to experience without requiring

00:11:34.220 --> 00:11:36.140
them to visit a
whole separate page.

00:11:36.140 --> 00:11:38.515
And we think this will be
really helpful for the hundreds

00:11:38.515 --> 00:11:40.100
of millions of
users who are coming

00:11:40.100 --> 00:11:43.670
online with slower connections.

