the home pages in the store,

00:12:07.070 --> 00:12:09.470
and also in the My Apps
section of the store,

00:12:09.470 --> 00:12:12.992
where users are already coming
in to manage app updates.

00:12:12.992 --> 00:12:15.394
That's a super early phase
of the project right now,

00:12:15.394 --> 00:12:17.060
but we're sharing it
with you because we

00:12:17.060 --> 00:12:19.340
think it's an important
part of driving engagement

00:12:19.340 --> 00:12:21.980
and stickiness
with Android games.

00:12:21.980 --> 00:12:23.490
So that's about it for me today.

00:12:23.490 --> 00:12:25.310
I hope each of you
are a little bit more

00:12:25.310 --> 00:12:28.220
convinced that Google is
serious about supporting

00:12:28.220 --> 00:12:30.290
the quality of the
Android gaming experience

00:12:30.290 --> 00:12:32.630
from our hardware to
the operating system,

00:12:32.630 --> 00:12:35.780
from our Developer
Tools to the Play Store.

00:12:35.780 --> 00:12:39.140
And we know that in order
to keep our users happy,

00:12:39.140 --> 00:12:41.450
we depend on developers
like you to keep creating

00:12:41.450 --> 00:12:43.500
incredible gaming experiences.

