So I'd like to introduce Jamil
Moledina, our Games Strategic

00:12:46.820 --> 00:12:49.220
Lead, who will announce a
set of exciting titles coming

00:12:49.220 --> 00:12:50.768
to the platform.

00:12:50.768 --> 00:12:55.124
[APPLAUSE]

