"Pokemon Go," the hit augmented
reality game from Niantic,

00:15:28.320 --> 00:15:30.690
driven by Google Maps
and Google Cloud,

00:15:30.690 --> 00:15:33.930
got people across the
globe off the couch

00:15:33.930 --> 00:15:36.630
and out catching Pokemon.

00:15:36.630 --> 00:15:38.430
Fans were screaming for more.

00:15:38.430 --> 00:15:41.560
And here to give us a
little of what we want

00:15:41.560 --> 00:15:43.390
