00:22:15.450 --> 00:22:17.760
Please join me in welcoming
Jeff Howell and Mike

00:22:17.760 --> 00:22:18.880
McCartney from Kabam.

00:22:18.880 --> 00:22:22.808
[APPLAUSE]

00:22:28.209 --> 00:22:29.820
MIKE MCCARTNEY: Thanks Jamil.

00:22:29.820 --> 00:22:31.910
We're really excited
to be here and show off

00:22:31.910 --> 00:22:36.600
Kabam's next free-to-play AAA
quality game, "TRANSFORMERS,

00:22:36.600 --> 00:22:38.250
Forged to Fight."

