So whether you're a fan
of the classic generations

00:22:46.590 --> 00:22:50.290
characters, characters from
the Transformers movies,

00:22:50.290 --> 00:22:52.560
or even the Maximals and
Predacons from the Beast Wars

00:22:52.560 --> 00:22:54.900
series, our game
has you covered,

00:22:54.900 --> 00:22:58.830
featuring intense one-versus-one
combat, deep strategic RPG

00:22:58.830 --> 00:23:02.250
systems, and engaging
social gameplay.

