Here we go.

00:24:48.446 --> 00:24:50.170
JEFF HOWELL: All
right, it's time

00:24:50.170 --> 00:24:52.999
to show what real
transformation is about.

00:24:52.999 --> 00:24:54.290
Let's finish off Optimus Prime.

