operation, you'll have

00:38:22.920 --> 00:38:25.240
to tell the rabbits
by shaking your head

00:38:25.240 --> 00:38:27.780
if you want the object
back in your body or not.

00:38:32.034 --> 00:38:33.700
So you probably want
to keep your heart.

00:38:44.032 --> 00:38:47.910
[END PLAYBACK]

00:38:47.910 --> 00:38:50.250
LOIC GOUNON: That's
a nice image.

