00:39:25.390 --> 00:39:28.230
We are eager to have you try
out our game at Google Daydream

00:39:28.230 --> 00:39:30.100
booth starting Wednesday.

00:39:30.100 --> 00:39:31.037
Thank you.

00:39:31.037 --> 00:39:35.510
[APPLAUSE]

